description: Aspose.Tasks for .NET is a .NET Project management component that enables .NET applications to not only read and manipulate Microsoft Project documents in MPP and XML formats but to also write Microsoft Project documents in MPP or Project XML format - all without using Microsoft Project.
releaseNotes:
New Features
TASKS-33154 - Write updated Resource data back to MPP file
TASKS-33159 - Write updated data to MS Project 2007 MPP file
TASKS-33155 - Write updated Task data back to MPP file
TASKS-33156 - Write TaskLink data back to MPP file
TASKS-31064 - Write updated Calendars data back to MPP file
TASKS-20136 - Write updated outline codes definitions and values back to MPP files
TASKS-20135 - Write updated extended attributes definitions and values back to MPP file

Bugs
TASKS-33153 - [Obfuscated DLL with C++] Unable to use obfuscated Aspose.Tasks.dll with C++
summary: Aspose.Tasks for .NET is a component to work with Project files
title: Aspose.Tasks for .NET
